# Roam Research Source

Joel's `egghead-roam-research` repository is a high-value source for pi-notes because it contains a historical Roam export plus deterministic analyses of graph/process behavior.

## Source location

Remote source on panda:

```txt
~/Code/joelhooks/egghead-roam-research
```

Canonical dataset:

```txt
egghead-2026-01-19-13-09-38.edn
```

The source repository's safety rule says the EDN export is read-only and generated outputs should be written as new files.

